divs: Sighting DetailsWhile outside to view meteor showers observed object directly above. Immediately thought it was a triangle shaped object. Object drifted slowly S.E. over the horizon. I watched it for at least 3 minutes. Went back inside, told my wife about the object and drew a sketch along with some notes. Than you, TWT
